Package it.polimi.ingsw.model.messages

  • Class Summary
    Class Description
    BoughtCardUpdate
    Update sent after the player has successfully bought a development card.
    ChatUpdate
    Update sent when a player wants to broadcast a new chat message.
    CreateMarketUpdate
    Update sent upon creation of the market, after starting the game.
    DepositStrongboxUpdate
    Update sent after modification of the player's strongbox
    DepositUpdate
    Update sent after a modification of the player's deposit.
    DevelopmentDeckUpdate
    Update sent after a development card has been removed by the deck
    EndGameUpdate
    Update sent after the game has ended.
    EndSingleplayerGameUpdate
    Update sent when a single player game ends.
    FaithUpdate
    Update sent upon modification of a player's faith.
    GamePhaseUpdate
    Update sent after a game phase change
    InitialTurnUpdate
    Updates sent for the initial turn.
    InvalidActionUpdate
    Update sent when a Player performs an invalid action.
    LastRoundUpdate
    Update sent when the last round begins, after a player has ended the game by finishing the faith track or buying 7 cards.
    LorenzoActionUpdate
    Update sent after Lorenzo performs an action, in single player mode.
    LorenzoFaithUpdate
    Update sent upon modification of Lorenzo's faith points (in single player mode).
    MarketResultUpdate
    Update sent to the player that has drawn from the market.
    MarketUpdate
    Update sent upon modification of the market.
    OwnedLeadersUpdate
    Update sent upon modification of the player's leader cards (after initial draw, activation or discard of one of them)
    PlayerPropertyUpdate
    Update regarding modifications of one player's properties.
    PopeFavourUpdate
    Update sent upon modification of one player's gained pope favours.
    PropertyUpdate
    Update sent upon modification of one property of the game.
    TurnUpdate
    Update sent when the turn shifts towards the next player in the playing order.
